      • addDirectory

        public boolean addDirectory(File directory)
        Adds a directory to the local store in a thread-safe manner All necessary parent directories must exist prior to invoking this method
        Parameters:
        directory - a File that represents the directory to add to the store, which currently must not exist
        Returns:
        true if the directory was added, false otherwise
        Throws:
